name: 阿纳斯塔西娅·扎巴尔丘克
name_full: 阿纳斯塔西娅·扎巴尔丘克 Anastasia Zabarchuk
introduction: Ana Zab is an Argentinian actress of Russian and Ukrainian descent. Born in Yekaterinburg, Russia, she moved to London, United Kingdom at 18, where she studied politics for a few years before deciding to pursue her dream and starting a career in acting. She has been a part of over 50 productions, both big and small, ranging from commercials to big-budget movies and TV series.
